d51 2
a52 4
   * Test if the installation was successful:
      1 Go to <nop>TopicClassification within the web where you've unzipped the %TOPIC% archive. See if it lists the following <nop>TopicTypes: <nop>SubjectArea, <nop>TopicType, <nop>ReferenceTopic.
      1 *Important:* Go to <nop>WebFormWithClassification and edit WebForm to include pertinant elements from this template, or if there is no existing WebForm topic, simply rename this topic to WebForm. Make sure you have enabled the the WebForm in WebPreferences.
      1 Go to <nop>CreateNewTopic and create your first <nop>SubjectArea topic.  
